.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, mango, onion, watermelon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, thriller, time-travel
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, alhambra, chaman, swisher
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 2. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the swisher-smoker##5
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the dannemann-smoker##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
 6. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
 7. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the dannemann-smoker##7
 8. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
11. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | apricot   | onion       | watermelon    | mango      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel | crime         | thriller   |
| Cigar   | swisher   | dannemann  | alhambra       | chaman |
| Sport         | golf      | volleyball  | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

