.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, blues, trance, techno
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the fan of techno is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 4. the person drinking sprite is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person watching crime movies##6
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 8. the fan of blues is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 9. the fan of blues is the person watching crime movies##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
11. the fan of country is not the person watching crime movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | soy-milk       | mirinda         | sprite       |
| Hobby         | cooking     | video-games    | rock-climbing   | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre           | techno   | blues | trance | country     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire      | crime          | drama           | martial-arts |

