.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, bongani, oliveros, game
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, fisherman, musician, videographer
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the musician is the oliveros-smoker##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is between the game-smoker and the bongani-smoker##2
 5. the architect is somewhere to the right of the bongani-smoker##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the musician and the dannemann-smoker##7
 7. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
10. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the architect is somewhere to the right of the bongani-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Cigar   | game      | oliveros     | bongani   | dannemann    |
| Job     | videographer | musician   | fisherman | architect |
| Pet     | snake        | rabbit     | goldfish  | pony      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 